399
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:07,960
Consagrado internacionalmente,
名扬世界的贝利,

400
00:27:08,079 --> 00:27:09,560
Pelé se torna alvo
de grandes times europeus,
成了欧洲大牌球队竞相招揽的目标,

401
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:10,800
(Juventus and Milan disputano Pelé)
