852
00:53:30,484 --> 00:53:33,043
Ele tirou o pé enganando Jair Varilho,
他抬起脚,骗过Jair Varilho,

853
00:53:33,165 --> 00:53:35,203
Cafu acompanhou a corrida de Jair,
