855
00:53:39,320 --> 00:53:43,082
provocando aplausos
de toda a torcida do Maracanã.
引发Maracanã体育场所有球迷的喝彩.

856
00:53:43,202 --> 00:53:45,042
O estádio se levantou,
体育场观众都站起身,

857
00:53:45,161 --> 00:53:47,280
